&lt;h1 id="play-stupid-games-win-stupid-prizes"&gt;Play Stupid Games, Win Stupid Prizes&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;May 17 2019&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competition will blind you to greater games&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nivi:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;When you&amp;rsquo;re being authentic, you don&amp;rsquo;t mind competition that much. It pisses you off and inspires some fear, jealousy and other emotions. But you don&amp;rsquo;t really mind because you&amp;rsquo;re oriented towards the goal and the mission. Worst-case, you might get some ideas from them. And often there are ways to work with the competition in a positive way that ends up increasing the size of the market for you.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>